y\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/tests/test_exceptions.py`\n  - *Verify:* Each exception can be instantiated and has correct attributes\n\n- [ ] **T033** Write unit tests for ControlPlaneClient\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/tests/test_control_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* create_session, delete_session work correctly\n\n- [ ] **T034** Write unit tests for CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* All operations make correct HTTP requests\n\n- [ ] **T035** Write unit tests for CodeInterpreterClient\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/tests/test_code_interpreter_client.py`\n  - *Verify:* Full lifecycle, context manager, error handling\n\n- [ ] **T036** Create example usage scripts\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/examples/basic_usage.py`\n  - *Verify:* Demonstrates CodeInterpreterClient usage\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| T002 | T001 |\n| T003 | T001 |\n| T004 | T001 |\n| T005 | T001, T002, T003 |\n| T006 | T005 |\n| T007 | T005 |\n| T008 | T005 |\n| T009 | T001, T003 |\n| T010 | T009 |\n| T011 | T009 |\n| T012 | T010, T011 |\n| T013 | T010, T011 |\n| T014 | T010, T011 |\n| T015 | T010, T011 |\n| T016 | T010, T011 |\n| T017 | T009 |\n| T018 | T001, T002, T003, T005 |\n| T019 | T018 |\n| T020 | T005, T009 |\n| T021 | T020 |\n| T022 | T020, T026 |\n| T023 | T020 |\n| T024 | T020, T023 |\n| T025 | T020 |\n| T026 | T017, T007 |\n| T027 | T018, T029 |\n| T028 | T005, T009, T030 |\n| T029 | T001, T003 |\n| T030 | T001, T003 |\n| T031 | T029 |\n| T032 | T002 |\n| T033 | T005, T006, T007 |\n| T034 | T009-T017 |\n| T035 | T018-T026 |\n| T036 | T018 |\n\n---\n\n## Verification Checklist\n\n- [ ] AC001: CodeInterpreterClient constructs with proper defaults (name, namespace, ttl, verbose)\n- [ ] AC002: CodeInterpreterClient creates session via ControlPlaneClient when session_id not provided\n- [ ] AC003: CodeInterpreterClient supports context manager protocol with proper cleanup\n- [ ] AC004: Code