{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867735862,"sessionID":"ses_2860b2284ffeKRyyLhi5s5T4BC","part":{"id":"prt_d79f65d1e001nW2oR7nMPZ4sNE","messageID":"msg_d79f652dd001n94KXpAbYhwsuZ","sessionID":"ses_2860b2284ffeKRyyLhi5s5T4BC","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_7e46c9e295e941ada4a47456","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Tasks\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete - Implementation Pending)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Project Structure & Utilities (T001-T004)\n\n- [ ] **T001** Create `pyproject.toml` for `agentcube-sdk` package with dependencies: `requests`, `PyJWT>=2.0.0`, `cryptography`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/pyproject.toml`\n  - *Verify:* Package builds with `python -m build`, requires Python >=3.10\n\n- [ ] **T002** Create `agentcube/exceptions.py` with exception hierarchy\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/exceptions.py`\n  - *Verify:* `AgentCubeError`, `CommandExecutionError(exit_code, stderr, command)`, `SessionError`, `DataPlaneError` all defined; `CommandExecutionError` is subclass of `AgentCubeError`\n  - *Test:* Import and instantiate each exception\n\n- [ ] **T003** Create utility modules: `agentcube/utils/http.py`, `agentcube/utils/utils.py`, `agentcube/utils/log.py`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/http.py` - `create_session()` with HTTPAdapter\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/utils.py` - `read_token_from_file(file_path) -> str`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/log.py` - `get_logger(name, level) -> logging.Logger`\n  - *Verify:* All functions importable and work as specified in design.md\n\n- [ ] **T004** Create `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` module marker\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/utils/__init__.py`\n  - *Verify:* Empty file, creates valid Python package\n\n---\n\n### Phase 2: Control Plane Client (T005-T008)\n\n- [ ] **T005** Implement `ControlPlaneClient` class with constructor\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Accepts `workload_manager_url`, `auth_token`, `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0`, `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n  - *Test:* Instantiate client, verify default values\n\n- [ ] **T006** Implement `ControlPlaneClient.create_session(name, namespace, metadata, ttl)` \n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* POSTs to `{base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` with JSON body, returns `sessionId` from response\n  - *Test:* Call create_session, verify correct HTTP request and response parsing\n\n- [ ] **T007** Implement `ControlPlaneClient.delete_session(session_id)`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* DELETE to `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}`, returns `True` on 404, logs and returns `False` on other failures\n  - *Test:* Test 404 response returns True\n\n- [ ] **T008** Implement `ControlPlaneClient.close()`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Closes HTTP session\n  - *Test:* Verify session is closed after close() call\n\n---\n\n### Phase 3: Code Interpreter Data Plane Client (T009-T017)\n\n- [ ] **T009** Implement `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` class with constructor\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Accepts `session_id`, `router_url`, `namespace`, `cr_name`, `base_url`, `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0`, `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n  - *Test:* Instantiate with router_url+namespace+cr_name, verify base_url constructed correctly\n\n- [ ] **T010** Implement base URL construction from router components\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* When `base_url` not provided, constructs `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/code-interpreters/{cr_name}/invocations/\")`\n  - *Test:* Verify correct URL format\n\n- [ ] **T011** Implement `_request()` helper with session header\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Adds `x-agentcube-session-id: {session_id}` header to all requests\n  - *Test:* Make request, verify header present\n\n- [ ] **T012** Implement `execute_command(command, timeout)` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* POSTs to `api/execute` with JSON `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"<n>s\"}`, read_timeout = timeout + 2.0\n  - *Test:* Execute command, verify request format\n\n- [ ] **T013** Implement `write_file(content, remote_path)` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* POSTs to `api/files` with base64 encoded content, path, mode \"0644\"\n  - *Test:* Write file, verify request body format\n\n- [ ] **T014** Implement `upload_file(local_path, remote_path)` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* POST multipart form data to `api/files` with `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n  - *Test:* Upload file, verify multipart request\n\n- [ ] **T015** Implement `download_file(remote_path, local_path)` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* GET `api/files/{clean_path}` with `stream=True`, writes to local path\n  - *Test:* Download file, verify stream handling\n\n- [ ] **T016** Implement `list_files(path=\".\")` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* GET `api/files` with query parameter `path`\n  - *Test:* List files, verify query param\n\n- [ ] **T017** Implement `close()` method\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Closes HTTP session\n  - *Test:* Verify session closed\n\n---\n\n### Phase 4: Code Interpreter Client (T018-T026)\n\n- [ ] **T018** Implement `CodeInterpreterClient` class with constructor\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* Accepts `name=\"my-interpreter\"`, `namespace=\"default\"`, `ttl=3600`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `auth_token`, `verbose=False`, `session_id=None`\n  - *Test:* Instantiate client, verify defaults\n\n- [ ] **T019** Implement router URL validation\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* Raises `ValueError` if neither `router_url` argument nor `ROUTER_URL` env var is set\n  - *Test:* Instantiate without router_url, verify ValueError raised\n\n- [ ] **T020** Implement `_init_data_plane()` and session creation\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* If no `session_id` provided, calls `cp_client.create_session()`, then initializes data plane client\n  - *Test:* Instantiate without session_id, verify create_session called\n\n- [ ] **T021** Implement data plane init failure handling\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* If `_init_data_plane()` fails after session created, logs warning, deletes session, sets session_id to None, re-raises\n  - *Test:* Simulate failure, verify cleanup\n\n- [ ] **T022** Implement context manager protocol (`__enter__`, `__exit__`)\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* `__exit__` calls `stop()`, which closes data plane and deletes control plane session if it was created by this client\n  - *Test:* Use client as context manager, verify cleanup on exit\n\n- [ ] **T023** Implement `execute_command(command, timeout)`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* Delegates to data plane client, raises `CommandExecutionError` on non-zero exit code\n  - *Test:* Execute command with exit code != 0, verify exception\n\n- [ ] **T024** Implement `run_code(language, code, timeout)`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* For python/py/python3, writes timestamped `.py` file, executes with `python3`\n  - *Test:* Run python code, verify execution\n\n- [ ] **T025** Implement file operations (`write_file`, `upload_file`, `download_file`, `list_files`)\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* Delegate to data plane client methods\n  - *Test:* Each operation works correctly\n\n- [ ] **T026** Implement `stop()` method\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/code_interpreter.py`\n  - *Verify:* Closes data plane session, deletes control plane session if created by this client\n  - *Test:* Call stop, verify cleanup\n\n---\n\n### Phase 5: Package Exports (T027-T028)\n\n- [ ] **T027** Create `agentcube/__init__.py` with public exports\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - *Verify:* `__all__ = [\"CodeInterpreterClient\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\"]`, imports both classes\n  - *Test:* `from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient`\n\n- [ ] **T028** Create `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` with client exports\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n  - *Verify:* `__all__ = [\"ControlPlaneClient\", \"CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\", \"AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\"]`\n  - *Test:* `from agentcube.clients import ControlPlaneClient`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 6: AgentRuntimeClient Stub (T029-T031)\n\n- [ ] **T029** Implement `AgentRuntimeClient` class stub\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* Basic class structure per design.md (full implementation in AR-028)\n  - *Test:* Instantiate client\n\n- [ ] **T030** Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` class stub\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Basic structure per design.md (full implementation in AR-028)\n  - *Test:* Instantiate client\n\n- [ ] **T031** Add AgentRuntimeClient to package exports\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - *Verify:* Already exported in T027\n  - *Test:* Import and use\n\n---\n\n### Phase 7: Integration & Tests (T032-T036)\n\n- [ ] **T032